                    ],
                    "effect": "You mentally impart the book\u2019s knowledge to your ally, giving them the benefit of the  *mnemonic feather* .",
                    "traits": [
                        {
                            "name": "Auditory",
                            "type": "trait",
                            "alternate_link": {
